to delete the file).

Was your file inconsistent ? When restarting you might be using the -refresh 
setting which triggers a refresh from local...

The navigator was in sync with the file system at the time. I did a refresh 
local at one point and I still got the error.

I could not reproduce in build 20020404. Did you have the problem lately? If 
not, I will close.
Go ahead. I haven't seen it since.
